    "summary": "In this transcript, a user expresses concern about missing a dose of Lisinopril and asks if they should double their dose to compensate. The assistant repeatedly and correctly advises against doubling the dose, explains the risks of hypotension (low blood pressure), and directs the user toward professional medical resources like an after-hours nurse line or urgent care.",
